### Machine configuration options

| Machine name        | vCPU | Memory | Disk space |
| ------------------- | ---- | ------ | ---------- |
| micro               | 0.25 | 0.25   | 10GB       |
| small-1x (default)  | 0.5  | 0.5    | 10GB       |
| small-2x            | 1    | 1      | 10GB       |
| medium-1x           | 1    | 2      | 10GB       |
| medium-2x           | 2    | 4      | 10GB       |
| large-1x            | 4    | 8      | 10GB       |
| large-2x            | 8    | 16     | 10GB       |

